title: KAIST School of Computing - Spring 24’ Grad School Info Session for International Students
content:
There will be an information session about KAIST SoC grad school for international students on Thursday at 7PM.
If you’re interested in pursuing MS/PHD degrees in KAIST SoC, please come join us the session to find out more information. Foods are provided for offline participants, and quiz winners will receive Starbucks gift cards！
Please note that this session is only for international students. Korean nationals must refer to regular admission tracks (Spring and Fall 2024).
Registration - please fill out this registration form to attend the session
https://forms.gle/WDYsyYfk2XwdWDQr5
Time : Aug. 10 (Thu), 2023, 7:00 PM KST
Venue: Room 201, IT Convergence Building (N1), KAIST (Dinner provided)
Zoom:
https://bit.ly/3XQSxpD
Application Periods: August 24 - September 14, 2023
